text: Vusal Aliyev (; born on 14 September 1970) is an Azerbaijani football referee. ==Biography== He refereed in Azerbaijan Premier League since 2002.Azərbaycanlı hakim karyerasını rəsmən başa vurdu - FOTO. apasport.az, 27.05.2015 He is a UEFA category referee.AZƏRBAYCANLI FUTBOL HAKİMİ ÇEXİYA-LİXTENŞTEYN OYUNUNU İDARƏ EDƏCƏKDİR. azertag.az, 30.07.2007 ==UEFA Euro 2008 Qualifying== ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:Living people Category:Azerbaijani football referees Category:People from Nakhchivan Category:1970 births
